The same goes for Zhuo Bufan.

104
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:06,879
Speaking of which,

105
00:07:06,879 --> 00:07:08,160
Zhuo Bufan and the people behind him

106
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:10,360
are more anxious than us
and Mr. Cunqing.

107
00:07:11,680 --> 00:07:12,519
After several battles,

108
00:07:12,519 --> 00:07:13,480
the leverage in his hands

109
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:15,800
is still the Discipline Seal.

110
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:17,399
But now we know

111
00:07:17,399 --> 00:07:18,600
that there are not only one

112
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:19,959
or two seals.

113
00:07:20,639 --> 00:07:22,360
So, regarding the clues for the treasure

114
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,680
Zhuo Bufan has made no progress

115
00:07:23,680 --> 00:07:24,879
and not gained any advantage at all.

116
00:07:25,240 --> 00:07:26,600
We seemed to return without success.

117
00:07:26,600 --> 00:07:28,399
In fact, we've ascertained
all the forces involved.

118
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:31,079
I've also kept Liu Lin by my side.

119
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:32,839
If we can't get information,

120
00:07:32,839 --> 00:07:34,759
others won't either.

121
00:07:35,959 --> 00:07:38,279
If someone
from Tongmenghui finds Liu Lin,

122
00:07:38,279 --> 00:07:39,920
we can take the chance
to catch them all at once.

123
00:07:41,160 --> 00:07:41,879
That's right.

124
00:07:43,040 --> 00:07:45,160
Zhuo Bufan is definitely eager
to find the seal.

125
00:07:45,160 --> 00:07:47,199
And the people behind him
will be eager to help him.

126
00:07:47,519 --> 00:07:48,240
They're anxious,

127
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:49,240
so we don't need to be.

128
00:07:49,920 --> 00:07:52,079
We're not waiting for the fruit

129
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:53,879
but we're waiting at ease.

130
00:07:53,879 --> 00:07:55,399
It's the best choice right now.

131
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:02,319
I have no clues.

132
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:04,319
You have

133
00:08:04,920 --> 00:08:05,920
been there.

134
00:08:06,800 --> 00:08:09,639
After the Imperial Household Department
failed in treasure hunting,

135
00:08:10,199 --> 00:08:12,079
this matter is on hold.

136
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:14,959
And the records are ambiguous.

137
00:08:15,959 --> 00:08:17,360
I don't believe

138
00:08:18,319 --> 00:08:19,680
that there's no chance

139
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:22,000
to find the treasure.

140
00:08:22,199 --> 00:08:23,480
You're right.

141
00:08:23,839 --> 00:08:24,920
To be frank,

142
00:08:25,120 --> 00:08:25,879
there is one thing,

143
00:08:27,079 --> 00:08:28,279
but it's not a clue.

144
00:08:28,759 --> 00:08:30,000
An old story.

145
00:08:30,199 --> 00:08:31,399
You can investigate it.

146
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:32,879
What is it?

147
00:08:33,519 --> 00:08:34,759
Xu He, the chief inheritor

148
00:08:34,759 --> 00:08:38,080
of the Disciplinary Department
of Southern Shaolin, turned to the court.

149
00:08:38,080 --> 00:08:39,360
He told me something.

150
00:08:39,679 --> 00:08:40,639
He said

151
00:08:40,639 --> 00:08:44,840
that he had seen the third generation
of Dharma Department's chief inheritor.

152
00:08:45,559 --> 00:08:47,080
The inheritor was a Nian rebel.

153
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:48,559
In 1865,

154
00:08:48,799 --> 00:08:49,759
it was he

155
00:08:49,759 --> 00:08:51,919
who killed Sengge Rinchen

156
00:08:51,919 --> 00:08:53,840
during the Caozhou battle

157
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:56,320
against the elite Mongolian cavalry.

158
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:58,200
In 1868,

159
00:08:58,440 --> 00:09:00,679
the Eastern Nian Rebellion was besieged
by Li Hongzhang's Huai Army.

160
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:02,039
The breakout failed,

161
00:09:02,679 --> 00:09:03,759
and the army was annihilated.

162
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:07,360
At that time, the inheritor
was seriously injured.

163
00:09:08,360 --> 00:09:10,000
He turned to his fellow.

164
00:09:10,559 --> 00:09:11,600
But he did not know

165
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:14,600
that his fellow had sided
with the court.

166
00:09:14,919 --> 00:09:18,399
So right after the inheritor
entered his house,

167
00:09:18,919 --> 00:09:21,519
the people from the Department arrived.

168
00:09:22,919 --> 00:09:25,519
Six masters led dozens of guards

169
00:09:25,759 --> 00:09:27,480
to ambush him.

170
00:09:28,919 --> 00:09:32,399
(However, the inheritor's kung fu
was formidable.)

171
00:09:32,960 --> 00:09:34,039
(He was wounded)

172
00:09:34,360 --> 00:09:35,399
(in the ambush)

173
00:09:35,480 --> 00:09:36,960
(but resisted desperately.)

174
00:09:37,240 --> 00:09:39,559
(He killed the defected chief
of the Disciplinary Department)

175
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:41,360
(and many guards.)

176
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:43,759
(He escaped from the hands)

177
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:45,200
(of the six masters.)

178
00:09:50,240 --> 00:09:53,039
(The six masters chased after him)

179
00:09:54,720 --> 00:09:57,000
(all the way to Tianning Temple
in Dongying.)

180
00:09:57,399 --> 00:09:59,440
(Eventually, in the nearby suburbs,)

181
00:09:59,440 --> 00:10:00,559
(they intercepted him.)

182
00:10:01,039 --> 00:10:02,600
(Both sides engaged in a bloody battle.)

183
00:10:03,039 --> 00:10:05,559
(Four of the six masters died.)

184
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:09,039
(The inheritor was struck
by 19 strokes,)

185
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:12,200
(fell into the river,
and was swept away by the water.)

186
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:15,240
By the water?

187
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:17,240
They didn't find his body?

188
00:10:17,919 --> 00:10:18,432
No.

189
00:10:20,960 --> 00:10:23,039
Fall into the river?

190
00:10:23,879 --> 00:10:25,960
So no one knows if he is dead or alive.

191
00:10:26,159 --> 00:10:26,879
Yes.

192
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:30,840
How skilled were the six masters

193
00:10:31,080 --> 00:10:32,320
in martial arts?

194
00:10:32,320 --> 00:10:33,320
One of them

195
00:10:33,799 --> 00:10:36,440
is Luan Yi,
the later high-ranking imperial guard.

196
00:10:36,679 --> 00:10:37,679
The other one

197
00:10:38,639 --> 00:10:39,360
is me.

198
00:10:41,360 --> 00:10:42,720
A master, indeed.

199
00:10:42,879 --> 00:10:45,080
Back then, to avoid future troubles,

200
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:46,720
Luan Yi and I

201
00:10:46,720 --> 00:10:49,279
searched along the river for many days

202
00:10:50,200 --> 00:10:51,679
till the estuary.

203
00:10:52,679 --> 00:10:54,200
But we did not find his body.

204
00:10:55,159 --> 00:10:58,039
But when you reported back
to the Imperial Household Department,

205
00:10:58,039 --> 00:11:00,559
you said you killed that person.

206
00:11:00,600 --> 00:11:02,879
We were young and afraid of punishment.

207
00:11:03,200 --> 00:11:05,519
After all,
it was a complete annihilation.

208
00:11:06,159 --> 00:11:07,679
If we could not kill that person,

209
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:09,080
we were to blame.

210
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:12,639
Over these 43 years,

211
00:11:12,879 --> 00:11:14,679
Luan Yi and I have always felt

212
00:11:15,159 --> 00:11:18,240
that we failed to kill that inheritor.

213
00:11:20,000 --> 00:11:21,639
It's been over 40 years.

214
00:11:22,039 --> 00:11:23,919
Even if that person is still alive,

215
00:11:24,120 --> 00:11:26,159
he should be
in his sixties or seventies.

216
00:11:26,360 --> 00:11:27,159
So,

217
00:11:27,759 --> 00:11:29,159
this is not a clue.

218
00:11:29,519 --> 00:11:30,840
It's just an old story.

219
00:11:32,679 --> 00:11:34,600
You brought it up.

220
00:11:35,519 --> 00:11:37,360
Because it's an old issue,

221
00:11:38,080 --> 00:11:40,240
it may not have been properly resolved.

222
00:11:41,799 --> 00:11:42,759
Your Highness is wise.

223
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:50,399
Dharma's chief.

224
00:11:50,960 --> 00:11:51,840
Dharma Seal.

225
00:11:53,080 --> 00:11:55,399
Investigate it in the Tianjin Presidio.

226
00:11:56,639 --> 00:11:57,840
This person's surname is Zhang.

227
00:11:58,480 --> 00:12:00,960
If he's still alive,

228
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:04,320
he should be
in his sixties or seventies.

229
00:12:05,639 --> 00:12:07,039
I have already

230
00:12:07,480 --> 00:12:08,879
found the clue you wanted.

231
00:12:09,799 --> 00:12:12,399
May I meet the two surviving masters
from the imperial yamen?

232
00:12:13,600 --> 00:12:14,840
The two people

233
00:12:15,360 --> 00:12:17,559
didn't die 43 years ago.

234
00:12:17,639 --> 00:12:20,279
Do you think
they could still be alive now?

235
00:12:21,480 --> 00:12:23,799
Since it's an incomplete clue
from 43 years ago, how do I

236
00:12:24,120 --> 00:12:25,039
continue the investigation?

237
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:27,759
Zhao Fu.

238
00:12:30,240 --> 00:12:30,816
Your Highness.

239
00:12:31,679 --> 00:12:32,320
Your Highness.

240
00:12:32,720 --> 00:12:33,600
Get to the point.

241
00:12:35,440 --> 00:12:38,240
I used to be a clerk
in the Tianjin Presidio.

242
00:12:39,039 --> 00:12:40,159
20 years ago,

243
00:12:40,159 --> 00:12:43,440
I joined the annals of the counties
surrounding Tianjin Presidio.

244
00:12:44,399 --> 00:12:46,080
On the outskirts of Wuqing County,

245
00:12:46,799 --> 00:12:48,679
I ran into an old madman.

246
00:12:48,679 --> 00:12:50,120
He was delirious.

247
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:54,399
But he told people
that he was a martial arts expert,

248
00:12:54,399 --> 00:12:55,399
a grandmaster,

249
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:57,879
thus he became a laughingstock.

250
00:12:58,159 --> 00:13:00,279
I was interested in him.

251
00:13:01,039 --> 00:13:01,879
So I observed him.

252
00:13:02,679 --> 00:13:05,080
I happened to see him catching rabbits
in the wilderness.

253
00:13:05,600 --> 00:13:06,679
He moved swiftly.

254
00:13:07,240 --> 00:13:08,360
It's baffling.

255
00:13:09,480 --> 00:13:10,440
The old lunatic

256
00:13:11,399 --> 00:13:12,799
was homeless.

257
00:13:13,120 --> 00:13:14,080
The wilderness,

258
00:13:14,320 --> 00:13:15,240
ruins,

259
00:13:15,440 --> 00:13:16,279
streets,

260
00:13:16,600 --> 00:13:17,519
and the bushes

261
00:13:17,720 --> 00:13:19,639
were all his shelter.

262
00:13:20,200 --> 00:13:21,039
Some said

263
00:13:21,919 --> 00:13:23,799
he painstakingly

264
00:13:23,799 --> 00:13:25,480
picked fresh fruits

265
00:13:25,679 --> 00:13:28,559
and took them to temples to pay respect.

266
00:13:29,639 --> 00:13:30,480
I believe

267
00:13:31,039 --> 00:13:31,919
he is not ordinary.

268
00:13:34,200 --> 00:13:34,759
You may leave.

269
00:13:38,879 --> 00:13:40,600
Such clues

270
00:13:41,480 --> 00:13:42,840
are incomplete for you?

271
00:13:51,159 --> 00:13:53,159
Sixi meatballs, crispy pork,

272
00:13:53,159 --> 00:13:54,879
pork with sauce, sauteed shredded pork,

273
00:13:54,879 --> 00:13:55,519
mixed vegetables,

274
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:57,720
and f-fried sheep fillet?

275
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:00,159
Give it a try.

